short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The easiest way to copy GitHub labels between repositories.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When working in multiple project, I have trouble when defining labels for each repository, it take a lot of time. My idea is to create this extension to help people to easy to clone GitHub labels between repositories.
